            <h4 class="title">Worldwide Olympic Partnership</h4>
          
	        <div class="content">
	            <p><p>Bridgestone Americas is proud to be an official TOP Worldwide Olympic Partner of the International Olympic Committee (IOC), as well as a partner of the United States Olympic Committee and U.S. Paralympics. Learn more about how these partnerships provide unparalleled opportunities to showcase the company’s passion for performance and commitment to community service, social responsibility, environmental stewardship, and sustainability – all tenets of the Olympic Charter that mirror Bridgestone’s core values. To learn more, please visit <a href="http://www.bridgestoneperformance.com/en" target="_blank">BridgestonePerformance.com</a></p>
</p>
	        	
      				
			 	    
