<div class="component-card-easterEgg ">
  
    <div class="easterEgg-image" style="background-image: url(/content/dam/bscorpcomm-sites/bridgestone-americas/images/homepage/EarthDay2016_easterEgg.jpg)">
    </div>
  
  <div class="easterEgg-details">
    <div class="easterEgg-columnWrapper">
      

      <h2 class="easterEgg-title">Bridgestone Americas Celebrates Earth Day</h2>
      <div class="easterEgg-content">
        <p>At Bridgestone Americas, our environmental mission is to help ensure a healthy environment for current and future generations. We’re proud of our company’s efforts to create programs and initiatives aimed at being in harmony with nature, valuing our natural resources and reducing CO2 emissions. Under our One Team, One Plant program, we’re focused on identifying ways we can change the game by being a leader in sustainable corporate behavior.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>This Earth Day, we’re encouraging our teammates to practice greener habits at home as well. From enhancing the garden to increasing recycling efforts to switching to LED lighting, there are many simple steps we can take in our daily lives to make a big difference in the future of our plant.</p>
<p>Click below to see our Earth Day infographic.&nbsp;<a name="_GoBack"></a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
    
      <div class="easterEgg-cta">
        <a href="/en/newsroom/brand-assets/infographics#/Gallery2016/2016%20Infographics" class="button button-default">Infographic</a>
      </div>
    
  </div>

  
  <div class="easter-egg-button close-easter-egg button button-default">
    <div class="icon-accordion-minus">
